        <main class="w-full bg-[#FBF5F0] max-w-[1920px] px-[20px] md:px-[10px] lg:px-[190px] xl:px-[150px] m-auto">

            <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center py-[70px]">

                <div class="max-w-[1142px] w-full bg-white px-[10px] py-[10px] shadow-lg flex flex-col gap-[20px] text-justify">

                    <h1 class="text-[merriweather] text-[28px] text-[#000000]">Shipping and Delivery Policy</h1>
                
                    <dl class="space-y-8">
                        <!-- Shipping and Delivery Policy Overview -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                1. Shipping and Delivery Policy Overview
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Geldix Pharmaceuticals Private Limited is committed to delivering your orders in a timely and
                                efficient manner. This Shipping and Delivery Policy outlines the terms and conditions related to the
                                shipment and delivery of products purchased from our website.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                
                        <!-- Shipping and Delivery Charges -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                2. Shipping and Delivery Charges
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Shipping and delivery charges are calculated based on the total weight of your order, the delivery
                                location, and the shipping method chosen at checkout. Any applicable charges will be displayed at
                                checkout before you complete your purchase.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                
                        <!-- Processing and Delivery Timeframes -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                3. Processing and Delivery Timeframes
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Orders are typically processed within 1-2 business days. Delivery times may vary depending on your
                                location, but we aim to deliver orders within 5-7 business days. Please note that these timeframes
                                are estimates and may be affected by factors beyond our control.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                
                        <!-- Order Tracking -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                4. Order Tracking
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with a tracking number.
                                You can use this tracking number to monitor the status of your delivery on the courier's website.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                
                        <!-- Shipping Restrictions -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                5. Shipping Restrictions
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Currently, we only ship to addresses within India. We do not deliver to P.O. boxes, APO/FPO addresses,
                                or international locations. Please ensure that the shipping address provided is accurate and complete
                                to avoid delays.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                
                        <!-- Damaged or Lost Items -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                6. Damaged or Lost Items
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                If your order arrives damaged or is lost in transit, please contact us immediately at
                                <a href="mailto:info@geldix.in?subject=Damaged product while shipping&body=Hello Geldix Pharmaceuticals" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600">info@geldix.in</a>
                                with your order details. We will work with the shipping carrier to resolve the issue and provide a
                                replacement or refund as necessary.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                
                        <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                7. Changes to This Policy
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                Geldix Pharmaceuticals Private Limited reserves the right to modify this Shipping and Delivery Policy
                                at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page and will take effect immediately. Please review
                                this policy periodically to stay informed about our shipping and delivery practices.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                
                        <!-- Contact Information -->
                        <div>
                            <dt class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
                                8. Contact Information
                            </dt>
                            <dd class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
                                If you have any questions or concerns about this Shipping and Delivery Policy, please contact us at
                                <a href="mailto:info@geldix.in?subject=Question about shipping and delivery policy&body=Hello Geldix Pharmaceuticals" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600">info@geldix.in</a>
                                or visit our office at
                                <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/7iSA9uBCFWpqXsrh8" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600">
                                    Shop 2, Katara Hills, Rapadia Village, 462043, Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India
                                </a>.
                            </dd>
                        </div>
                    </dl>
                
                </div>
                

            </div>

